720
01:05:26,800 --> 01:05:30,720
'You mean -' said Bella 
Slattery. 'But that's impossible.  

721
01:05:31,760 --> 01:05:35,840
The royal family always have police and 
detectives around them, don't they?'

722
01:05:36,640 --> 01:05:42,000
'You only need one terrorist with a bomb, 
in the right crowd at the right time. At two  

723
01:05:42,000 --> 01:05:47,440
o'clock this afternoon,' replied Harriet. 
'I was investigating Free People, you see.  

724
01:05:48,560 --> 01:05:52,800
And when I discovered their plan, they 
took Liam, to stop me warning the police.  

725
01:05:53,840 --> 01:05:58,640
It's difficult for me, isn't it? If 
I warn the police, Free People will  

726
01:05:58,640 --> 01:06:03,840
kill Liam - and say that he died because his 
mother, his family, chose not to save him.  

727
01:06:04,400 --> 01:06:08,960
But if I don't warn the police, there will be 
several deaths in another, more famous family.  

728
01:06:10,000 --> 01:06:16,080
And Free People will say that they died because 
of my love for my son, my family. Either way,  

729
01:06:16,080 --> 01:06:20,080
Free People win the game, because the 
idea of the family gets bad publicity.'

730
01:06:21,120 --> 01:06:23,760
She put her head in her hands and sat very still.

731
01:06:24,880 --> 01:06:29,440
Joe stood up. 'I understand now. We'll help you.'

732
01:06:30,560 --> 01:06:35,120
'But -' said Keith miserably, 'shouldn't we 
tell the police about the bomb before we start?'

733
01:06:36,240 --> 01:06:40,320
'Yes,' said Harriet. She was 
finding it difficult to speak.  

734
01:06:41,440 --> 01:06:46,080
'I decided yesterday to warn the 
police. So the royal family are  

735
01:06:46,080 --> 01:06:50,800
safe. But Liam will be dead after two 
o'clock, if we don't get him out.'
 
 

736
01:06:51,840 --> 01:06:56,240
11.00 A.M.
Doyle had gone out and Tug was washing  

737
01:06:56,240 --> 01:07:01,840
the breakfast dishes when there was a knock on the 
door. The Woman hid the guns and opened the door.  

738
01:07:02,880 --> 01:07:05,040
It was the girl who had come with the policeman.

739
01:07:06,000 --> 01:07:08,640
'Hallo, Mrs Doyle,' the girl said politely.  

740
01:07:09,760 --> 01:07:15,440
'We just wanted to invite you to our harvest 
party this evening. It's very good fun -' She  

741
01:07:15,440 --> 01:07:21,040
