driving fast down the road away from the cottage.

748
01:07:58,800 --> 01:08:05,840
'So what's your plan, Doyle?' asked the Woman. She 
had her gun in her hand, and was ready to shoot.

749
01:08:06,880 --> 01:08:12,000
'You'll see. We're going somewhere safe 
for the next two or three hours - Oh no!'

750
01:08:13,040 --> 01:08:18,800
There were four men walking along the road towards 
them. Doyle drove faster, straight at them,  

751
01:08:18,800 --> 01:08:23,840
